{"tid":2146464,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新界牛嘅我唔見咗隻狗","createTime":"2020-08-08T14:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T21:33:21.000Z","uid":216398,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"32f91c85be294293a30ba1654c31ca113c0fc0fe","tid":2146464,"uid":216398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我就住係元朗新田個邊啲村屋嘅 隻狗就奶油色嘅法國老虎嚟 極少會吠 肥肥地 2歲幾左右 痴人唔怕生 咩人都撚得 有打晶片<br />\n<br />\n  應該今日4點幾左右時間走失咗 事源應該係個裝修師傅搬嘢冇check好對門有冇閂實 隻狗係對門到走咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  之前試過幾次偷走都係好近附近嘅地方搵到 但今次好肯定佢走咗去條出村大馬路到之後唔見 搵咗幾個鐘都冇 懷疑比人偷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n  隻狗有抽筋個啲問題 要定期食藥 <br />\n<br />\n  如果有人見過我隻狗唔該各位巴絲打幫下手話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  我知道唔見隻狗我有責任 但依一刻真係好想搵返隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdeb8cab8e3ef4fba7ccff7ece6874bd647a6364","tid":2146464,"uid":43594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec13ad95f0df76e83544ede41316c1f12ce2a512","tid":2146464,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5608f872e1ab77f4d687241f73fe24429b3dba0f","tid":2146464,"uid":343080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nbtw巴打啲腳毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff7233819434b924e0f767907c54adeb9c2221","tid":2146464,"uid":93277,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"放過隻狗啦，你平時對佢好又點會走?"},{"pid":"8507ea9bbec451ff78aac71688b6ca881528d5bb","tid":2146464,"uid":228143,"like":0,"d